post_text: Staff and students are collecting and donating gift cards (Vons/Safeway, Arco etc.) for families in Butte County. Paradise no longer has a school- they’ve lost EVERYTHING!!! Superintendent Barry Simpson will personally deliver the gift cards to the Superintendent of Butte County Schools. Please drop gift cards off at any of the Bishop Schools or the District Office. Visit our website for a complete list of gift cards needed. Thank you!

post_text:
Students and Staff at BUSD held their "Students Supporting Cancer Awareness" campaign and the "Shine on the Sierra Luminary Walk" during the week of October 23-28. Many events took place on campus and we were able to raise close to $5550.00 for our local Eastern Sierra Cancer Alliance.
Thank you everyone!
